anl.verdi.area.target

Class ProjectionInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component
      • java.awt.Container
        • javax.swing.JComponent
          • javax.swing.JPanel
            • anl.verdi.area.target.ProjectionInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible

    public class ProjectionInfo
extends javax.swing.JPanel
    Generic GUI widget that allows user to enter parameters for the selected projection.
    Supported projections:
  • Lambert Conformal Conic
  • Mercator
  • Transverse Mercator
  • Polar Stereographic
  • XY (Simple Scaling)
